      <title>
         <ph props="autonumber">237.7603</ph> Solicitation provision and contract clause.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a) Use the clause at 
               <xref href="252.237-7023.dita#DFARS_252.237-7023" base="i1383682" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">252.237-7023</xref>
            , Continuation of Essential Contractor Services in all solicitations and contracts for services that are in support of mission-essential functions.</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b) Use the provision at 
               <xref href="252.237-7024.dita#DFARS_252.237-7024" base="i1383692" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">252.237-7024</xref>
            , Notice of Continuation of Essential Contractor Services in all solicitations for services that include the clause 
               <xref href="252.237-7023.dita#DFARS_252.237-7023" base="i1383682" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">252.237-7023</xref>
            .</p>
